  "detailed_description": "C&T is a<strong> Goofy Team-Strategy Multiplayer game</strong> where you play either as a <strong>cop</strong> trying to <strong>catch thieves</strong> or a thief trying to <strong>run away from the cops</strong> in the small town of Rundown Browntown.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959380/extras/3d68e22fce412a70efc1c9a36f4639a8.avif?t=1671716191\" width=500 height=138 /></span><br><br><br><strong>2 teams</strong> in a western map. <strong>Fast paced games</strong> where the cops have to arrest all the thieves within 5 minutes.<br><strong>Thieves can release each other</strong> within a small window of time after getting caught. Each player receives a <strong>random perk</strong> at the start of each round.<br><strong>Invent new strategy each game with a multitude of insane perks!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959380/extras/f330979f43b904bb1207baa0edeb055f.avif?t=1671716191\" width=500 height=138 /></span><br><br>The <strong>server list</strong> is always available so you can <strong>create your own games</strong> or <strong>join games</strong> of other players.<br>You can make your games <strong>public </strong>if you don't have any friends or <strong>private</strong>, to play with your imaginary friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959380/extras/3ab0fd419ea13c47430cebf166380ce8.avif?t=1671716191\" width=500 height=138 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "C&T is a<strong> Goofy Team-Strategy Multiplayer game</strong> where you play either as a <strong>cop</strong> trying to <strong>catch thieves</strong> or a thief trying to <strong>run away from the cops</strong> in the small town of Rundown Browntown.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959380/extras/3d68e22fce412a70efc1c9a36f4639a8.avif?t=1671716191\" width=500 height=138 /></span><br><br><br><strong>2 teams</strong> in a western map. <strong>Fast paced games</strong> where the cops have to arrest all the thieves within 5 minutes.<br><strong>Thieves can release each other</strong> within a small window of time after getting caught. Each player receives a <strong>random perk</strong> at the start of each round.<br><strong>Invent new strategy each game with a multitude of insane perks!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959380/extras/f330979f43b904bb1207baa0edeb055f.avif?t=1671716191\" width=500 height=138 /></span><br><br>The <strong>server list</strong> is always available so you can <strong>create your own games</strong> or <strong>join games</strong> of other players.<br>You can make your games <strong>public </strong>if you don't have any friends or <strong>private</strong>, to play with your imaginary friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959380/extras/3ab0fd419ea13c47430cebf166380ce8.avif?t=1671716191\" width=500 height=138 /></span>",
